{"tid":1174162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"危機升級：任正非透露製作了兩萬個「不死的華為」獎章","createTime":"2019-05-27T15:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T12:09:18.000Z","uid":20058,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"3d6c538fe9199caebb993780ecd3149f039b7d92","tid":1174162,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T15:45:25.000Z","msg":"內地傳媒報道，華為創辦人任正非在接受訪問時說：「我們已經製作了兩萬枚獎章，上面寫是『不死的華為』，我們根本不認為會死，為甚麼把死看得那麼重呢？我們梳理一下問題，哪些去掉，哪些加強，勝利一定是屬於我們的。高端產品美國也沒辦法，我們完全靠自己，不靠美國。」<br />\n<br />\n他又說：「美國今天把我們從北坡往下打，我們順着雪往下滑一點，再起來爬坡。但是總有一天，兩軍會爬到山頂。我們理想是為人類服務，又不是為了賺錢，又不是為了消滅別人，大家共同能實現為人類服務不更好嗎？今天有人說5G將來會不會分裂成兩種標準，西方一種、東方一種，我認為不會，因為人類好不容易統一了一個標準，為共同的全球雲社會服務，兩種標準就是兩朵雲，這個東西將來是很難交融。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/30NHCyQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30NHCyQ&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQRR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=c1c52630\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/30NHCyQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e63e23e6a843425f5324abb09b1b67428ffd03","tid":1174162,"uid":130695,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T15:48:15.000Z","msg":"出口術就叻 華為製造電子垃圾第一"},{"pid":"510b33500e179992435da05d5c1213c97312f35b","tid":1174162,"uid":93986,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T15:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RmG1MEq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRmG1MEq.gif&h=81721175&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c73fb9ec7a0f73b98d1c27f250da689485b88b9","tid":1174162,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T15:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6641d766051cb165408ec7a84a7625ab8ae2e31f","tid":1174162,"uid":7369,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T15:51:12.000Z","ms